---

This package bundles sqlite-vec (https://github.com/asg017/sqlite-vec), an
unmodified C amalgamation vendored at Sources/CSQLiteVec/sqlite-vec.c and
Sources/CSQLiteVec/sqlite-vec.h. sqlite-vec is dual-licensed MIT OR
Apache-2.0, at the user's option -- the full texts are reproduced verbatim
in Sources/CSQLiteVec/LICENSE-MIT and Sources/CSQLiteVec/LICENSE-APACHE.
See THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md for complete third-party attribution.
